	PMT 17-20 => MPD4 №5 => MADC №2 ch 1-8
	PMT 21-24 => MPD4 №6 => MADC №2 ch 9-16
	PMT 25-28 => MPD4 №7 => MADC №2 ch 17-24
	PMT 29-32 => MPD4 №8 => MADC №2 ch 25-32

